OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed following the
OL,7,Fdeath of 21 year-old Ryan Sandhu in a
OL,8,Fcollision in the city centre.
OL,10,FRyan was driving on the A38 (M) Aston
OL,11,FExpressway just after midnight on
OL,12,FSunday 2 June 2024.
OL,14,FHis car was smashed into by an Audi,
OL,15,Fwhich caused it to hit another car,
OL,16,Fand was confirmed dead at the scene.
