OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,FThe Audi was driven by 28-year-old
OL,7,FSaqlane Zafar. He had been speeding
OL,8,Fthrough closed lanes along the
OL,9,Fexpressway, causing traffic to swerve
OL,10,Fout of the way.
OL,12,FThe car was travelling at 91mph when
OL,13,Fit crashed into Ryan's car, when the
OL,14,Fspeed limit was 40mph.
OL,16,FFurther investigations revealed that
OL,17,Fobjects had been thrown from the Audi
OL,18,Fover the barrier of the expressway,
OL,19,Fand officers later recovered a number
OL,20,Fof nitrous oxide cannisters from the
OL,21,Froad below.
