OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,FThe Audi had been travelling together
OL,7,Fwith a Nissan, being driven by 28-year-
OL,8,Fold Muhammad Hamza.
OL,10,FFollowing the collision, Hamza briefly
OL,11,Fstopped to pick up Zafar, and the pair
OL,12,Ffled the scene of the crash.
OL,14,FThe Nissan then failed to stop for
OL,15,Fofficers in Small Heath but following
OL,16,Fa pursuit, the two men were detained,
OL,17,Fand Zafar was found to still have the
OL,18,Fhire agreement in his name for the
OL,19,FAudi involved in the crash.
