OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,FZafar was arrested, charged, and
OL,7,Fsubsequently pleaded guilty to causing
OL,8,Fdeath by dangerous driving.
OL,10,FHamza was arrested and charged with
OL,11,Fdangerous driving and perverting the
OL,12,Fcourse of justice, and was found
OL,13,Fguilty of both following a trial at
OL,14,FBirmingham Crown Court.
OL,16,FOn Friday (23 January), Zafar was
OL,17,Fsentenced to a total of 15 years in
OL,18,Fprison, while Hamza was jailed for
OL,19,Ffour years and six months.
