OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,FIn a new statement following the
OL,7,Fsentencing, Ryan's family said:
OL,9,F"This is a long-overdue affirmation of
OL,10,Fthe truth, something we have carried
OL,11,Fwith us since the moment our lives
OL,12,Fwere shattered when we lost Ryan.
OL,13,FWhile we are relieved and grateful
OL,14,Fthat justice has finally been served,
OL,15,Fwe cannot ignore the pain and insult
OL,16,Fwe endured throughout this process,
OL,17,Fparticularly as we endured the
OL,18,Fheartbreak of a not guilty plea that
OL,19,Fdenied us the reality of what happened.
