OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,F"The denial of responsibility for such
OL,7,Fa clear and devastating act was more
OL,8,Fthan just a legal tactic. It was an
OL,9,Finsult to our family, to the memory of
OL,10,FRyan, and to common decency. It forced
OL,11,Fus to relive our worst moments, while
OL,12,Fthose responsible denied
OL,13,Faccountability.
OL,15,F"With a guilty verdict and this
OL,16,Fsentencing, let us be reminded that
OL,17,Faccountability matters. Victims and
OL,18,Ftheir families will not be silenced.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
