OL,3,CTwo jailed over death of man killed in
OL,4,Ccity centre collision
OL,6,F"We are incredibly thankful to the
OL,7,Fprosecution team, police, and the
OL,8,Fjurors for their dedication and
OL,9,Fcommitment to serving justice.
OL,11,F"Most importantly, we will never stop
OL,12,Fhonouring Ryan's life ` a life that
OL,13,Fwas stolen, but never forgotten.
OL,15,F"Justice was delayed, but it was not
OL,16,Fdenied."
